que, ainsi que des petits conseils à l’attention des producteurs et des consommateurs, un glossaire spécifique, un QCM et une grille de mots fléchés figurant en fin d’ouvrage.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Biology.2bisacsh1 aMarouf, Abderrazak, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2022z9783110993134oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2022z978311076825140uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-2730-540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759827305423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759827305/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076825-1  EDP Sciences Frontlist eBook Package 2022b2022  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2022  aZDB-23-DPMb2022